{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — cart delivery panel (Phase 2.11C → 2.11F).

  Compact, premium, mobile-first cart delivery summary, rendered at the top of the
  cart (drawer + page) when the cart has items. Populated client-side by
  assets/ganguram-delivery-progress.js from window.GanguramDeliveryRules + the
  selected location. Starts hidden; shows only when an admin delivery rule resolves.
  data-gdpr-cart-total carries the live cart total in PAISE. Display/advisory only.

  2.11F: the MAIN area is intentionally short — a status line, compact delivery-mode
  chips, a theme-coloured MOV progress bar, and a short action line. Everything
  detailed (pincode, zone, cart value, MOV, per-mode charge, the checkout note) lives
  ONCE inside the collapsed "Delivery details" accordion. The pincode is NOT shown as
  a prominent repeated headline. No hardcoded colours — see the CSS (theme variables).

  Accepts: context = 'drawer' (compact) | 'page' (detailed).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign gdpr_context = context | default: 'drawer' -%}
<div class="ganguram-delivery-progress ganguram-delivery-progress--{{ gdpr_context }}" data-ganguram-delivery-progress data-gdpr-cart-total="{{ cart.total_price }}" data-gdpr-context="{{ gdpr_context }}" hidden>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__prompt" data-gdpr-prompt role="status" hidden></p>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__status" data-gdpr-status hidden></p>
  <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__modes" data-gdpr-modes hidden></div>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__mov-summary" data-gdpr-mov-summary hidden></p>
  <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" data-gdpr-bar hidden>
    <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__bar-fill" data-gdpr-bar-fill></div>
  </div>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__message" data-gdpr-message hidden></p>
  <p class="ganguram-delivery-progress__fourhour-notice" data-gdpr-fourhour-notice role="status" hidden></p>
  <details class="ganguram-delivery-progress__breakdown" data-gdpr-breakdown hidden>
    <summary class="ganguram-delivery-progress__breakdown-summary" data-gdpr-breakdown-title></summary>
    <div class="ganguram-delivery-progress__breakdown-body" data-gdpr-breakdown-body></div>
  </details>
</div>
